  "detail": {
    "labelNames": "经营资费规则",
    "pv": "1",
    "endLabelIds": "6314",
    "endLabelNames": "资费规则",
    "title": "京东开放平台商家保证金管理规则",
    "followRuleId": "638209647311982592",
    "content": "<h1 style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第一章 总则</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /></span><strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第一条</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">为保障消费者权益，规范商家经营行为，明确保证金的缴存、调整、补缴、赔付、划扣及退还等流程，依据平台相关协议，制定本规则。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong>第二条</strong>&nbsp;本规则适用于京东开放平台所有经营企业店的商家。</span></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二章 定义</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /></span><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第三条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">保证金是商家根据平台规则及协议约定缴存的资金，用于在商家未履行消费者保障义务、违反平台规则或协议时，向消费者进行赔付、向京东支付违约金或其他相关费用。保证金包括基础保证金、风险保证金和临时保证金。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第四条</strong>&nbsp;保证金可用余额指保证金总额扣除已赔付金额、暂扣金额后的剩余金额。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第五条</strong>&nbsp;保证金分类说明：<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（一）<strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">基础保证金</strong>：商家入驻时缴纳，用于担保商品质量、服务履约及协议履行。部分类目实行阶梯保证金制度，按月度成交金额（<span style=\"background-color: #ecf0f1;\">GMV</span>）分档补缴，具体档位及金额以《京东开放平台类目资费规则》为准。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（二）<strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">风险保证金</strong>：商家在经营中出现违规或风险行为（如延迟发货、虚假交易、售假等）时，基于风险评估收取，风险消除后予以退还。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（三）<strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">临时保证金</strong>：用于提升售后退款额度，商家可通过冻结钱包余额或充值后冻结的方式实时生效。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（四）<strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">保险保证金：</strong>指符合投保条件的商家，在入驻或经营过程中，选择以保险形式全部或部分替代现金缴纳的保证金。其中，选择全额保险的商家，在满足保险平台审核要求且钱包余额充足的前提下，其基础保证金的补缴将默认通过保险方式完成：应缴标准升高时自动划扣保费，降低时自动退还差额。保险生效期为一年，投保成功实时生效。具体使用规则见<a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: none; color: #3768fa; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/hot-topic/detail?issueId=47941.html\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: black;\">《<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #4e30f9;\">全额保证金保险产品服务规范</span>》</span></a>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 2; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第三章 保证金缴存</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /></span><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第六条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家应按平台要求以以下方式之一缴纳保证金：<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（一）现金缴纳；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（二）现金+保险方式缴纳。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第七条</strong>&nbsp;基础保证金按所经营类目及品牌的最高标准缴纳。新增类目或品牌时，如保证金标准高于原金额，须补缴差额。未约定类目或特殊合同的，基础保证金最低为500元。基础类目保证金规则详见《<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #4e30f9;\"><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: none; color: #4e30f9; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;btype=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">京东开放平台类目资费规则</a></span>》，基础品牌保证金规则详见《<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #4e30f9;\"><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: none; color: #4e30f9; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2621&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\">京东开放平台品牌保证金规则</a></span>》。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; line-height: 2; background-color: white; text-align: justify; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第八条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"> <span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">风险保证金金额根据商家违规情节、风险等级、主营特定风险类目综合评定，具体以商家后台提示为准。</span> </span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; line-height: 26.6667px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第九条</strong>&nbsp;保证金存续期间不产生利息。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第十条</strong>&nbsp;未足额缴纳保证金的，京东有权采取下列一项或多项限制：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（一）限制货款提现；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（二）限制商品发布；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（三）限制营销推广功能；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（四）搜索推荐降权；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（五）限制对应品牌商品上架；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（六）其他必要措施。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第四章 保证金调整</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /></span><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十一条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东可根据商家业务变化、违规情况等调整保证金金额，包括但不限于以下场景：<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（一）新增经营类目；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（二）阶梯保证金成交金额达到新档位；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（三）商家或其关联店铺发生违规，需提高保证金以覆盖可能产生的赔付及违约金；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（四）商家涉及第三方投诉、举报、诉讼或仲裁，导致京东可能遭受损失的；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（五）商家被判定为风险商家，加收风险保证金；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（六）商家曾因违规被清退后再次入驻。</span></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第五章 保证金划扣与赔付</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /></span><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十二条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家发生以下情形时，京东有权划扣保证金用于消费者赔付、违约金支付及损失赔偿：<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（一）未履行或延迟履行服务承诺；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（二）售假或商品质量不合格；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（三）虚假或夸大宣传；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（四）侵犯他人知识产权等合法权益；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（五）标错价无法发货；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（六）每一有效投诉按货款金额的300%（食品、保健品为1000%）暂扣保证金，每单不少于500元；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（七）其他违反平台规则、协议或可能给京东造成损失的情形。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第十三条</strong>&nbsp;违约单生效超过7个自然日未缴纳违约金的，京东有权从保证金中直接划扣。</span></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第六章 保证金补缴</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /></span><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十四条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">保证金余额不足时，商家应及时补缴，否则京东有权采取第三章第十条所列限制措施。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第十五条</strong>&nbsp;以下情形需按最高标准补缴保证金：<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（一）新增高保证金标准类目；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（二）成交金额达到阶梯保证金补缴档位；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（三）需缴纳品牌保证金。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />补缴操作路径：京麦后台-财务-保证金管理。商家可在3个自然日内完成缴费，逾期将影响钱包功能使用。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border-style: none; word-break: break-all;\" src=\"https://img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/365133/11/8977/102775/692eb7bfFb1bdc151/8fb19fcf74b87501.png\" width=\"800\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">阶梯保证金成交金额查询路径：</span></p>\n<ul style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 5pt 0px 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; list-style-type: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 5pt 0cm 0.0001pt 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">新版京麦：数据&mdash;京东商智&mdash;交易&mdash;交易特征&mdash;类目特征</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 5pt 0cm 0.0001pt 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">旧版京麦：京东商智&mdash;交易&mdash;交易特征&mdash;类目特征</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border-style: none; word-break: break-all;\" src=\"https://img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/359341/20/17546/80964/692e5202F1f43831b/324a8663309df34d.png\" width=\"800\" /><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第十六条</strong>&nbsp;保证金不足时，京东有权：<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（一）从待结货款中扣划补足；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（二）采取冻结货款、追究违约责任、中止服务、清退店铺等措施；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（三）在代付款项后向商家追偿。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第十七条</strong>&nbsp;商家应在保证金低于标准金额后的3个自然日内补足，逾期将限制店铺功能。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第十八条</strong>&nbsp;商家申请退店时，需先按照<a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; text-decoration-line: none; color: #3768fa; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: black;\">《<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #4e30f9;\">京东开放平台类目资费规则</span>》</span></a>补足保证金至标准金额，否则京东有权从未结货款中扣划。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第七章 保证金退还</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /></span><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第十九条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">退保路径同第十五条。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第一节 经营期间退还</strong><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第二十条</strong>&nbsp;商家经营期间可申请部分或全额退还保证金，同一时间仅可提交一个退还申请。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第二十一条</strong>&nbsp;部分退还：<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（一）基础保证金超出应缴金额的，每月可申请退还一次，需同时满足：</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;1. 所有售后、纠纷、赔付已处理完毕；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; color: black; font-size: 10pt;\">2. 销售类目质保期届满（具体质保期要求<a href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1189752107549462528\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #1400ff; text-decoration: underline;\">点击此处查看</span></span></a>）；</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3.&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">无待核销权益发票、无倒挂欠款、无在途风险保证金单据。</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（二）风险保证金在商家无违规且风险行为消除一段时间后自动退还。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第二十二条</strong>&nbsp;全额退还：<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（一）申请条件：</span></p>\n<ol style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px; list-style-type: none; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\">\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">所有订单已完结，售后、纠纷、赔付已处理；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">无未结算单据、无待核销发票、无欠款；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">退款账户状态正常，非保证金黑名单商家；</span></li>\n<li style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">完成30天休业公示，且所有销售类目质保期届满（具体质保期要求<span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #1400ff;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><a style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #1400ff; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" href=\"https://learn-jdm.jd.com/knowledge/rule/detail?ruleId=1189752107549462528\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">点击此处查看</a></span></span>）。符合条件后，京东在10个工作日内退还至商家钱包或原支付账户。</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（二）全额退保证金管控管控措施：申请全额退保后，店铺休业公示30天，商品全部下架，撤销申请可恢复经营。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第二节 退店后退还</strong><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第二十三条</strong>&nbsp;退店后退还：</span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-size: 10pt; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">（一）申请条件同第二十二条第一项；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（二）退款流程同第二十二条；<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" />（三）出现第十二条情形的，保证金不予退还。</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第八章 其他规定</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /></span><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二十四条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">若商家存在欠费，京东有权对商家店铺及关联店铺的剩余保证金余额（包含临时保证金）以及钱包余额等进行欠款抵扣。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二十五条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">保证金相关操作产生的银行手续费等第三方费用由商家承担。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第二十六条</strong>&nbsp;商家信息变更应提前30个自然日书面通知京东，否则由此导致的损失自行承担。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第二十七条</strong>&nbsp;商家应保证保证金来源合法，如由第三方代付，须提供相关证明文件。</span></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2; text-align: center;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第九章 附则</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; margin: 12pt 0cm; padding: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; color: #000000; white-space: normal; text-align: left; background-color: white; font-family: 等线; line-height: 2;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\"><br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /></span><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\"><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">第二十八条</span></strong><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本规则生效前的行为适用原规则，生效后的行为适用本规则。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第二十九条</strong>&nbsp;京东有权根据运营需要调整本规则并公示。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第三十条</strong>&nbsp;商家应遵守国家法律法规及平台协议，京东的处理不免除其法律责任。<br style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\" /><strong style=\"scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; word-break: break-all; max-width: 100%;\">第三十一条</strong> 本规则于2026年3月10日修订，2026年3月17日生效。</span></span></p>",
